{"tid":1591323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「認真討論」為左免被帶風向，我建議⋯⋯","createTime":"2019-09-24T06:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T09:11:26.000Z","uid":271367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0e85158dd98cc3335a0da6d5c26652e0cfa862cb","tid":1591323,"uid":271367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:03:21.000Z","msg":"8.31/新屋嶺/眾多不明屍體發現案-呢類案件受大家關注但又難fact check既事，預期係咁俾無公信力既政府隱瞞抹黑，不如我地歸類佢地做「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">觀察名單</span></span>」。<br />\n<br />\n我地不信政府的所謂真相，但又因為種種未可以讓民間流傳的真相公諸於世。所以要做一個清單做長期跟進。希望大家可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">集中力量</span></span>面對當下行動。<br />\n<br />\nP牌仔多謝你睇到呢一行。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命。</span></span>"},{"pid":"6ca56ac772089d87643a57934929a9f88dc0e6a1","tid":1591323,"uid":271367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"P仔無得推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a68db48e49835fff697c4b9ae9c51815a4e0d4","tid":1591323,"uid":73333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:08:14.000Z","msg":"風向依家好易帶起，尤其而家個個好火"},{"pid":"a086d24ed10ad4f0b7c12986409737cd3870af3e","tid":1591323,"uid":271367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6a68db48e49835fff697c4b9ae9c51815a4e0d4","tid":1591323,"uid":73333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:08:14.000Z","msg":"風向依家好易帶起，尤其而家個個好火"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"所以我先想提議整 觀察名單 。 人既力量好有限，要集中做先成事。分工好重要。"},{"pid":"ac5d309ed66fb680bd64b0cf0fa000b3d709b56d","tid":1591323,"uid":73333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:31:35.000Z","msg":"你見得我一個回你就知點解啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d4d1a234eb0a82f19ae0839b70d8b00fd42b2f","tid":1591323,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"